---
import ArticleLayout from '../layouts/ArticleLayout.astro';
---

<ArticleLayout
  title="Engineering Design | Wavey Dynamics"
  heading="ENGINEERING DESIGN"
  subheading="The art of arriving at design."
  image="/images/pages/engineering-development-hero.jpg"
  imagePosition="center 20%"
  description="Engineering design consultancy by Wavey Dynamics — 3D modelling, CAD, CFD, FEA, and design for manufacture for motorsport and high-performance automotive applications."
>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Understanding the benefit of providing a full service, the aspiration to deliver a seamless journey from initial concept through to continuous production and final design sign off is essential. Biomechanics and an exploration of vehicle engineering solutions is a passion of ours and our enthusiasm about this field makes us different.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">We draw considerable inspiration from the elegance of the natural world around us, and this runs through all our design capacities — our methods are efficient and sustainable design concepts.</p>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">In the interest of innovation, we can offer you:</p>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Design</h2>
  <ul class="wd-list mb-10 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>3D Model Generation</li>
    <li>2D Drawing/Drafting</li>
    <li>Vehicle Specification Design
      <ul class="wd-list-2 mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>With accommodation of full DOF</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Composite Design</li>
    <li>Surfacing</li>
    <li>Generative Design</li>
    <li>Reverse Engineering</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Simulation</h2>
  <ul class="wd-list mb-10 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD)
      <ul class="wd-list-2 mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Conductive/Convective heat transfer</li>
        <li>Fluid Flow</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Finite Element Analysis (FEA)
      <ul class="wd-list-2 mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Structural analysis</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Manufacture</h2>
  <ul class="wd-list mb-10 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>Design for Manufacture
      <ul class="wd-list-2 mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>3D printing</li>
        <li>G-Code/DXF</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Rapid Prototyping</li>
    <li>Prototyping</li>
    <li>Prototype Test &amp; Verification</li>
  </ul>

  <a href="/contact" class="inline-block border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors">Get in Touch →</a>

</ArticleLayout>
